{"tid":508620,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"乃木坂46討論區#61：聖誕快樂！！！","createTime":"2017-12-24T12:15:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-24T12:22:17.000Z","uid":3776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f7e018934e2bca78518475a94a15fbdb163d5b4e","tid":508620,"uid":3776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T12:15:56.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">LIHK乃PO呼籲:<br />\n「不要緊<br />\n你還有乃團」</span></span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/24/201548_98a961de0209bdc382782f192fb41f65.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F24%2F201548_98a961de0209bdc382782f192fb41f65.jpeg&h=9b25f2a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</div><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">乃木坂46(Nogizaka46)</span> 是一個日本大型女子偶像團體，為另一著名女子團體AKB48的「官方對手／正式對手」（公式ライバル），因此其行銷策略與AKB48的姐妹團體&mdash;&mdash;SKE48、NMB48、HKT48等不同，但總製作人同樣是秋元康，且與其他姊妹團體之間仍常有跨團體的合作或競賽企畫。團體名字中的「46」讀作「Forty-six／フォーティシックス」，而不是讀作「四十六／よんじゅうろく」。包含一期生、二期與三期生在內，團體目前共有46名成員，而隊長為櫻井玲香。<br />\n乃木坂46是作為AKB48的「官方對手」而成立的女子團體，因此跟AKB48的「姊妹團體」（如SKE48等）不同。例如團體不像AKB48及其姊妹團體般擁有AKB48劇場、NMB48劇場等專屬表演場地。團體名稱中的「乃木坂」是唱片公司日本索尼音樂（SME）總部大樓的所在地。<br />\n根據秋元康所說，<span style=\"color: red;\">「46」象徵：「就算人數比AKB48少，也具有不遜於AKB48的幹勁</span>」。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">成員名單:</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.nogizaka46.com/member/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nogizaka46.com%2Fmember%2F&d=sje3%2B0DU1fnT6lzq94Tz7G6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=9b99815d\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nogizaka46.com/member/</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">-NEWS-</div><br />\n</span></span><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"> 与田祐希ファースト写真集『日向の温度』<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">12月26日正式發售</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/lp5OLq3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Flp5OLq3.jpg&h=27fd4513&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"> 若月佑美１ｓｔ写真集 パレット<br />\n堀未央奈１ｓｔ写真集 君らしさ<br />\n新内眞衣１ｓｔ写真集 どこにいるの？<br />\n松村沙友理１ｓｔ写真集意外っていうか、前から可愛いと思ってた<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">發售中</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/DyL9o42.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FDyL9o42.jpg&h=0de4f4c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">乃木坂46 19thシングル「いつかできるから今日できる」<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">發售中</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/gZEj3cI.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FgZEj3cI.png&h=f71cc0e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">乃木坂46成員列表 19TH VER.(最新)</span></span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/1DTi5gV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F1DTi5gV.jpg&h=e09f27e9&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">乃木坂46三期生</span></span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/1RLx155.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F1RLx155.jpg&h=9a3ab035&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">歡迎新人加入</span></span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://nogizaka46-dc.com/sort/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnogizaka46-dc.com%2Fsort%2F&d=sje3%2B0DU1fnT6lzq94Tz7G6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=5d8ea351\" target=\"_blank\">http://nogizaka46-dc.com/sort/</a></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">請新/舊手足定期體檢，以便加入DD黨</span></span></div><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Q&amp;A</div></span></span><br />\n1）那乃木坂乃何許人也？<br />\n簡單來說，乃木坂是來自日本的偶像組合，演戲唱歌跳舞等全部都會參與，是正統全能型偶像。<br />\n<br />\n2）那裡可以購買乃木坂既有關產品（生寫、CD、海報、寫真集、演唱會等）？<br />\n一般來說，信和地庫會有存貨，不過價錢就...另外有不少商品需於官方WEBSHOP購入，不過這裡有機會提供代購,，要看看手足們的心情。<br />\n<br />\n3）這裡可否討論其他非46的成員？<br />\n我們一般不會阻止，但請適量討論。皆因這裡主要討論46GRP,你也可作理性討論，攻擊、黑其他成員,但請先作好世界大戰的準備。<br />\n<br />\n4）那麼我要如何見到乃木坂成員？<br />\n直接飛去日本參加握手會、演唱會，不要幻想他們來港舉辦握手會，因為此舉極為傻豬。詳細辦法請向手足查詢。<br />\n<br />\n5）除了46GRP,有什麼值得推薦?<br />\nNONE<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">TEMPLATE:</span></span><a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/17WaT3I7dwYQdmaT85JQnAJAzfBc9EXMXLKGLlpllO2E/edit?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F17WaT3I7dwYQdmaT85JQnAJAzfBc9EXMXLKGLlpllO2E%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=sje3%2B0DU1fnT6lzq94Tz7G6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=fb76c52f\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/17WaT3I7dwYQdmaT85JQnAJAzfBc9EXMXLKGLlpllO2E/edit?usp=sharing</a>"},{"pid":"7abde82796e04d41124dce04c09bf95f34edc58a","tid":508620,"uid":5601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T12:17:38.000Z","msg":"有2個 推邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20f041d26a1a190e2fe73b0f8553e8e8b3b628c4","tid":508620,"uid":3776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T12:17:52.000Z","msg":"各位今晚做好安全措施，平平安安，祝大家聖誕快樂<br />\n係時候朴暈自己<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"963fcbfdd8f6d7c87004176ea8687a332f433b3c","tid":508620,"uid":27307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T12:18:28.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"ce6ec5381b1fca31df9251b12750c1e430dc58cf","tid":508620,"uid":3776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T12:22:17.000Z","msg":"乃木坂46討論區#61: メリークリスマス<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/508619/page/1?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/508619/page/1?ref=ios</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n唔好意思<br />\n大家請移玉歩<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}